{"tid":1015621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 記者實測！香港僱主根本不願聘請60歳以上人士","createTime":"2019-02-10T07:12:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T04:34:35.000Z","uid":19454,"like":74,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"7982b437ea4352f084b184d146f1ee7e519b5a71","tid":1015621,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:12:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/543001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F543001&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BJLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=32f9b896\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F543001&h=fc87567a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/543001</a><br />\n<br />\n本月起長者綜援申領年齡由六十歲收緊至六十五歲，政府表示，是希望能鼓勵健全長者工作，但今時今日、六十歲以上人士，找工作是否那麼容易？政策是否如政府所說，有助釋放勞動力呢？<br />\n<br />\n既然勞福局局長這樣說，整條街也是招聘告示，記者找來六十四歲的他，到深水埗嘗試找一份樓面工作。前後嘗試過五份，沒有一份工作成功，余健鴻認為與自己的年齡有莫大關係。<br />\n<br />\n不露面又如何呢？記者再嘗試致電。打了五、六回電話，通通也沒有回音。詢問一下飲食業人士為何會這樣，有人指與年齡無關，是經驗問題。不過，經常協助六十歲以上人士找工作的社工說，僱主一聽到求職者是六十歲以上，大多都不願意聘請。<br />\n<br />\n梁錦添預計六十至六十四歲綜援人士參加自力更生計劃時，找工作會十分困難，社工要做更多功夫，例如游說僱主放寬聘用的年齡目標、以及開放更多工種，請較為年長的求職者。"},{"pid":"be837fd1b00fa3601aa822a03934ccc701bcc44d","tid":1015621,"uid":19454,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T07:13:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jCToTy0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjCToTy0.png&h=e3ed175d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tbD0VNm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtbD0VNm.png&h=47f4b3ee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2t75nsn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2t75nsn.png&h=e23b6b42&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gJC84FJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgJC84F